    "Its distribution in the training data is shown in Fig. 2.",
    "The data was split into the training and test parts: 80% (N=213) was used for training and 20% (N=54) was used to testing.",
    "The split was performed using stratified sampling on the discretized \"pledged amount\" variable, to ensure that the target variable has similar distributions in the training and in the test data.",
    "Keyword extraction Keywords were extracted using the RAKE Python package (Rose et al., 2010).",
    "RAKE's delimiter list was extended with additional parts-of-speech-verbs, adverbs, numerals, comparative and superlative adjectives, to give prominence to topical terms that commonly consists of nouns and adjectives."
